data.description: Coming soon on the market this beautiful colonial just in time for the holiday season. This would be a great gift to unwrap. More photos will be added soon, however there's some information about this beauty. Newer roof (2018), HVAC system (Payne unit June 2017), beautiful granite counters, updated cabinetry and full stainless steel appliance package (2017). Glistening wood floors throughout the living room into the dining room. Bathrooms were updated in 2017. Come and check it out.   Home is being sold 'as is". Seller is not able to make any repairs that may be required by the township. Buyer will be responsible to obtain the Certificate of Occupancy from Willingboro Twp.  Home inspection will be for informational purposes. Seller will not make any repairs that may be requested from the buyer's lender. Home is in fairly good condition, just the normal "wear and tear". Rugs on the second floor are stained.
